    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-body1",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "For structural steel and concrete buildings with other lateral-force-resisting systems,",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.06,
        "x_end": 0.48,
        "y_start": 0.05,
        "y_end": 0.08
      },
      "column": "left",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula1",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "na = 75/h",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.15,
        "x_end": 0.35,
        "y_start": 0.08,
        "y_end": 0.11
      },
      "column": "left",
      "expression": "n_a = \\frac{75}{h}",
      "parameters": [
        "n_a = approximate fundamental natural frequency",
        "h = height in feet"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula2",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "na = 22.86/h",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.15,
        "x_end": 0.35,
        "y_start": 0.11,
        "y_end": 0.14
      },
      "column": "left",
      "expression": "n_a = \\frac{22.86}{h}",
      "parameters": [
        "n_a = approximate fundamental natural frequency",
        "h = height in meters"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-body2",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "For concrete or masonry shear wall buildings, it is also permitted to use",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.06,
        "x_end": 0.48,
        "y_start": 0.15,
        "y_end": 0.18
      },
      "column": "left",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula3",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "na = 385(Cw)^0.5/h",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.15,
        "x_end": 0.35,
        "y_start": 0.18,
        "y_end": 0.21
      },
      "column": "left",
      "expression": "n_a = \\frac{385(C_w)^{0.5}}{h}",
      "parameters": [
        "n_a = approximate fundamental natural frequency",
        "C_w = 100\\sum_{i=1}^{n} \\left(\\frac{h_i}{h}\\right)^2 \\frac{A_i}{\\left[1 + 0.83\\left(\\frac{h_i}{D_i}\\right)^2\\right]}",
        "h = mean roof height, ft (m)",
        "n = number of shear walls in the building effective in resisting lateral forces in the direction under consideration",
        "A_B = base area of the building, ft^2 (m^2)",
        "A_i = horizontal cross-sectional area of shear wall i, ft^2 (m^2)",
        "D_i = length of shear wall i, ft (m)",
        "h_i = height of shear wall i, ft (m)"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-body02",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "where Iz is the intensity of turbulence at height z̄, and z̄ is the equivalent height of the building or structure defined as 0.6h, but not less than zmin, for all building or structure heights h. zmin and c are listed for each exposure in Table 26.11-1; gQ and gv shall be taken as 3.4. The background response Q̄ is given by",
      "cross_references": [
        "Table 26.11-1"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.2,
        "y_end": 0.28
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula4",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "na = 117.3(Cw)^0.5/h",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.15,
        "x_end": 0.35,
        "y_start": 0.21,
        "y_end": 0.24
      },
      "column": "left",
      "expression": "n_a = \\frac{117.3(C_w)^{0.5}}{h}",
      "parameters": [
        "n_a = approximate fundamental natural frequency",
        "C_w = 100\\sum_{i=1}^{n} \\left(\\frac{h_i}{h}\\right)^2 \\frac{A_i}{\\left[1 + 0.83\\left(\\frac{h_i}{D_i}\\right)^2\\right]}",
        "h = mean roof height, m",
        "n = number of shear walls in the building effective in resisting lateral forces in the direction under consideration",
        "A_B = base area of the building, m^2",
        "A_i = horizontal cross-sectional area of shear wall i, m^2",
        "D_i = length of shear wall i, m",
        "h_i = height of shear wall i, m"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-body3",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "where",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.06,
        "x_end": 0.12,
        "y_start": 0.24,
        "y_end": 0.26
      },
      "column": "left",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula13",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "Q = √(1/(1 + 0.63((B + h)/Lz)^0.63))",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.28,
        "y_end": 0.31
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "Q = \\sqrt{\\frac{1}{1 + 0.63\\left(\\frac{B + h}{L_z}\\right)^{0.63}}}",
      "parameters": [
        "Q = background response factor",
        "B = horizontal dimension of building perpendicular to wind direction, ft (m)",
        "h = mean roof height, ft (m)",
        "L_z = integral length scale of turbulence at the equivalent height",
        "B and h are defined in Section 26.3",
        "and Lz is the integral length scale of turbulence at the equivalent height given by"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula14",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "Lz = l(z̄/33)^ε",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.35,
        "y_end": 0.38
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "L_z = l\\left(\\frac{\\bar{z}}{33}\\right)^{\\varepsilon}",
      "parameters": [
        "L_z = integral length scale of turbulence at the equivalent height, ft",
        "l = terrain constant from Table 26.11-1, ft",
        "\\bar{z} = equivalent height, ft",
        "\\epsilon = terrain constant from Table 26.11-1"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula15",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "Lz = l(z̄/10)^ε",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.38,
        "y_end": 0.41
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "L_z = l\\left(\\frac{\\bar{z}}{10}\\right)^{\\varepsilon}",
      "parameters": [
        "L_z = integral length scale of turbulence at the equivalent height, m",
        "l = terrain constant from Table 26.11-1, m",
        "\\bar{z} = equivalent height, m",
        "\\epsilon = terrain constant from Table 26.11-1"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-body04",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "in which l and ε̄ are constants listed in Table 26.11-1.",
      "cross_references": [
        "Table 26.11-1"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.42,
