    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11.5-heading01",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11.5",
      "text": "26.11.5 Flexible Buildings or Other Structures For fl exible buildings or other structures as de fi ned in Section 26.2, the gusteffect factor shall be calculated by",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.44,
        "y_end": 0.47
      },
      "column": "right",
      "heading": true,
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11.5-heading01-body",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11.5",
      "text": "For flexible buildings or other structures as defined in Section 26.2, the gust-effect factor shall be calculated by",
      "cross_references": [
        "Section 26.2"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.45,
        "y_end": 0.47
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula16",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "Gf = 0.925((1 + 1.7Iz√(gQ²Q² + gR²R²))/(1 + 1.7gvIz))",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.47,
        "y_end": 0.5
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "G_f = 0.925\\left(\\frac{1 + 1.7I_z\\sqrt{g_Q^2Q^2 + g_R^2R^2}}{1 + 1.7g_vI_z}\\right)",
      "parameters": [
        "G_f = gust-effect factor for flexible buildings",
        "I_z = intensity of turbulence at height \\bar{z}",
        "g_Q = background peak factor = 3.4",
        "Q = background response factor",
        "g_R = resonant peak factor",
        "R = resonant response factor",
        "g_v = peak factor for wind speed = 3.4"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-heading1",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11.4",
      "text": "26.11.4 Rigid Buildings or Other Structures For rigid buildings or other structures as de fi ned in Section 26.2, the gust-effect factor shall be taken as 0.85 or calculated by this formula:",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.06,
        "x_end": 0.48,
        "y_start": 0.49,
        "y_end": 0.55
      },
      "column": "left",
      "heading": true,
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-heading1-body",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11.4",
      "text": "For rigid buildings or other structures as defined in Section 26.2, the gust-effect factor shall be taken as 0.85 or calculated by this formula:",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.06,
        "x_end": 0.48,
        "y_start": 0.5,
        "y_end": 0.55
      },
      "column": "left",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-body05",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "The background peak factors gQ and gv shall be taken as 3.4, and the resonant peak factor gR is",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.51,
        "y_end": 0.53
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula17",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "gR = √(2 ln(3600n1)) + 0.577/√(2 ln(3600n1))",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.53,
        "y_end": 0.56
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "g_R = \\sqrt{2\\ln(3600n_1)} + \\frac{0.577}{\\sqrt{2\\ln(3600n_1)}}",
      "parameters": [
        "g_R = resonant peak factor",
        "n_1 = fundamental natural frequency, Hz"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula5",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11.4",
      "text": "G = 0.925((1 + 1.7gQIzQ)/(1 + 1.7gvIz))",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.15,
        "x_end": 0.35,
        "y_start": 0.55,
        "y_end": 0.58
      },
      "column": "left",
      "expression": "G = 0.925\\left(\\frac{1 + 1.7g_Q I_z Q}{1 + 1.7g_v I_z}\\right)",
      "parameters": [
        "G = gust-effect factor",
        "g_Q = peak factor for background response = 3.4",
        "g_v = peak factor for wind speed = 3.4",
        "I_z = intensity of turbulence at height z",
        "Q = background response factor"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-body06",
      "type": "body",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "The background response factor, Q , and the intensity of turbulence at height z , I z , are de fi ned in Section 26.11.4. The resonant response factor is",
      "cross_references": [
        "Section 26.11.4"
      ],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.57,
        "y_end": 0.6
      },
      "column": "right",
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula6",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11.4",
      "text": "Iz = c(33/z)^(1/6)",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.15,
        "x_end": 0.35,
        "y_start": 0.58,
        "y_end": 0.61
      },
      "column": "left",
      "expression": "I_z = c\\left(\\frac{33}{z}\\right)^{1/6}",
      "parameters": [
        "I_z = intensity of turbulence at height z",
        "c = terrain exposure constant from Table 26.11-1",
        "z = equivalent height = 0.6h but not less than z_min"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "left"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula18",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11",
      "text": "R = √(1/β RnRhRB(0.53 + 0.47RL))",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.52,
        "x_end": 0.94,
        "y_start": 0.6,
        "y_end": 0.63
      },
      "column": "right",
      "expression": "R = \\sqrt{\\frac{1}{\\beta} R_nR_hR_B(0.53 + 0.47R_L)}",
      "parameters": [
        "R = resonant response factor",
        "\\beta = damping ratio, fraction of critical",
        "R_n = factor for along-wind response",
        "R_h = factor for across-wind response",
        "R_B = factor for torsional response",
        "R_L = factor for cross-correlation",
        "n_{1} is the fundamental natural frequency",
        "and \\beta is the damping ratio",
        "fraction of critical (e.g.",
        "for 2% use 0.02 in the equation)."
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
        "qc_status": "pending"
      },
      "_source": "right"
    },
    {
      "id": "ASCE7-22-26.11-formula7",
      "type": "formula",
      "section": "26.11.4",
      "text": "Iz = c(10/z)^(1/6)",
      "cross_references": [],
      "bbox": {
        "x_start": 0.15,
        "x_end": 0.35,
        "y_start": 0.61,
        "y_end": 0.64
      },
      "column": "left",
      "expression": "I_z = c\\left(\\frac{10}{z}\\right)^{1/6}",
      "parameters": [
        "I_z = intensity of turbulence at height z",
        "c = terrain exposure constant from Table 26.11-1",
        "z = equivalent height in meters = 0.6h but not less than z_min"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "extracted_by": "vision-clone",
